1
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,319
Apart from Shanhai City,

2
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,680
the other seven main cities

3
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,439
all have Immortal Gates rising into the sky.

4
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:22,719
So?

5
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,560
Have you ever considered

6
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:27,560
why only Shanhai City shows no anomaly,

7
00:01:27,719 --> 00:01:28,560
and what that means?

8
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,719
Father.

9
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:34,959
What does it mean?

10
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,640
In ancient times,

11
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,879
the sealed Celestial Realm

12
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:40,920
left eight Immortal Gates in our world.

13
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,640
If one day

14
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,120
the Immortal Gates appear,

15
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,280
pushing them open

16
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:47,040
can summon back the Celestial Realm.

17
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:48,200
As a boon,

18
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:51,319
the immortals will bless certain mortals,

19
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:53,519
granting them extraordinary powers.

20
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,159
If no Blessed appear in Shanhai City,

21
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:58,519
our status as a main city will be shaken.

22
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,680
So I've decided

23
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:02,120
to create a special team

24
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:04,040
to defend against

25
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,480
any crisis that may arise.

26
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,719
What do you think?

27
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,680
I told you,

28
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:15,879
when behind, just farm it out.

29
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:33,879
In such a confined space,

30
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:35,000
he's still full of energy.

31
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,520
Quite a surprise.

32
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,280
Come on down.

33
00:02:41,879 --> 00:02:43,599
The one I'm leading is Monkey.

34
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:46,280
He's a robber who looks fierce

35
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,759
but is actually a coward.

36
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:50,479
To verify my dream,

37
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:53,080
I joined the gang he was in.

38
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,560
Nobody move! This is a robbery!

39
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,599
Everyone, hands on heads, get down!

40
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:56,719
Get down! Don't move!

41
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,319
Pulling this at the Black Street Bank?

42
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,319
You two guards,

43
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:00,000
get down!

44
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,759
I said it's a robbery, are you deaf?

45
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:08,800
Number A006, please go to Window 3.

46
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,000
It matches! It matches!

47
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:18,240
It's exactly the same as in my dream.

48
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,879
Tie them up.

49
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,400
Tell the others to come pick them up.

50
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:32,319
In my dream, Monkey

51
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,919
will cross paths with me.

52
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,719
Cross paths how?

53
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:36,719
Can't quite remember.

54
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,560
Let's just grab him first.

55
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:39,719
Welcome to my place.

56
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:41,560
The busiest spot on Black Street,

57
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:42,439
with the worst

58
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,639
business of any shop.

59
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:45,639
How is it?

60
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,280
Does the name sound nice?

61
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,000
I thought long and hard

62
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,280
before coming up with

63
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:53,080
such a name full of healing virtue.

64
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,479
"Healing Hands of Wonder,

65
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:59,080
Snatching Souls Back from the Underworld."

66
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,240
Un... Underworld?

67
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,240
Don't be afraid.

68
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:04,800
As the only doctor on Black Street,

69
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,479
I'm very friendly,

70
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,319
very approachable.

71
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:10,319
Don't be fooled by outside rumors.

72
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,159
Move.

73
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:18,120
Where's the little cleaner?

74
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,399
Is she seeing another doctor again?

75
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:24,279
I'm clearly the best doctor here.

76
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,079
Can you clean?

77
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,519
No.

78
00:04:36,319 --> 00:04:37,319
If you can't clean,

79
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:39,360
how can you ever be a great robber?

80
00:04:40,519 --> 00:04:41,959
I... I'm a clean freak.

81
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,439
I'm the best at cleaning.

82
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,759
Clean the operating table well.

83
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,279
You'll be using it.

84
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:55,000
Thanks for your hard work.

85
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,240
I'll be using it?

86
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,560
Probably not enough beds.

87
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,800
Right, right, right.

88
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,680
You want me to sleep here,

89
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:04,720
sleep on top of this.

90
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:54,560
Nice to meet you.

91
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:57,160
I hope you like this gift.

92
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,920
This body

93
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,720
is truly a perfect vessel.

94
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:05,759
I look forward to your future massacres.

95
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,079
Remember me.

96
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,399
I'll come for you again.

97
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:12,040
Long-buried memories,

98
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:14,360
dug up once again?

99
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,759
Trying to strike a nerve?

100
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:20,439
This is far from enough.

101
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,360
You're awake.

102
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,720
You're not afraid of me?

103
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,079
I am.

104
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,920
Then why did you save me?

105
00:08:24,439 --> 00:08:27,279
Isn't saving lives the right thing to do?

106
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:29,480
This is Black Street.

107
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,639
But people from Black Street

108
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:32,960
are people too.

109
00:08:37,639 --> 00:08:38,320
You should go.

110
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,480
Okay.

111
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,320
Remember to drink plenty of water.

112
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,679
Thank you.

113
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:00,960
You're sick.

114
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,080
I know.

115
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,320
The doctor told me.

116
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:07,480
Why aren't you getting treatment?

117
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:08,960
I don't have any money.

118
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,320
The doctor kicked me out.

119
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,279
Clean this place for me.

120
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:13,879
I'll pay you.

121
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:15,279
Really?

122
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,320
I'll work hard.

123
00:09:17,639 --> 00:09:18,759
Don't you hate that doctor?

124
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:23,480
Charging for treatment is only fair.

125
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,960
I had no money.

126
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,399
So he had no obligation to let me stay.

127
00:09:27,879 --> 00:09:29,720
And my mom used to say,

128
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:32,639
if you look at the world with hatred,

129
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,679
then the world will seem dark.

130
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,600
As long as you try to smile,

131
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:39,120
the world won't do me wrong.

132
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,320
Little cleaner,

133
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,279
what's your name?

134
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:56,480
Is Tongtong the softest spot

135
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,519
in your heart?

136
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:03,960
If you saw Tongtong die before your eyes,

137
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,679
would it cause you pain?

138
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,399
Push open this door.

139
00:10:08,759 --> 00:10:09,759
Push it open.

140
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,639
Countless immortals will seek out

141
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:13,240
their compatible Blessed.

142
00:10:13,399 --> 00:10:14,159
At that time,

143
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:16,960
immortal seeds will form in the Blessed.

144
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:20,480
Seeds let mortals wield immortal power.

145
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,759
With the seed, I can save Tongtong.

146
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,320
Now that you've seen the Immortal Gate,

147
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,440
why not open it?

148
00:10:27,799 --> 00:10:29,159
Do you take me for a fool?

149
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:32,399
You now bear the Immortal Gate.

150
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:34,000
If the Gate doesn't open,

151
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:36,440
you won't find release either.

152
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,080
You're insane.

153
00:10:40,799 --> 00:10:42,320
Aren't you afraid of dying?

154
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,080
More than death,

155
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:49,360
I hate being threatened.

156
00:10:49,639 --> 00:10:51,480
Fine, we won't threaten you.

157
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,720
Everything's negotiable.

158
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:55,960
Actually, we can make a deal.

159
00:10:56,559 --> 00:10:58,360
Tongtong's illness is extremely rare.

160
00:10:58,879 --> 00:10:59,960
Even I

161
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:02,080
don't know its exact cause.

162
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,519
But I can guarantee one thing.

163
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,679
The immortal seed can save her.

164
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:08,519
At the very least,

165
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:10,639
it can slow down her illness.

166
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:28,200
Actually,

167
00:11:28,679 --> 00:11:30,559
if I open the Gate for just a moment

168
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,159
and then close it,

169
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,200
wouldn't that achieve the same result?

170
00:11:36,279 --> 00:11:36,919
Yes.

171
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,960
The moment the Immortal Gate opens,

172
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,320
the Celestial Realm descends,

173
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,399
blessing all living beings.

174
00:11:41,399 --> 00:11:43,279
And we are merely lonely spirits

175
00:11:43,279 --> 00:11:45,000
imprisoned within the Gate.

176
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:47,360
The moment the two realms connect,

177
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,600
we ourselves are of no importance.

178
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,200
But if the main gate stays sealed,

179
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,840
the immortals in the other seven gates

180
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,559
cannot regain their freedom either.

181
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:57,200
This karma is more than you can bear.

182
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:59,240
Even if you could bear it,

183
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:02,080
you couldn't close the Gate

184
00:12:02,159 --> 00:12:03,639
the instant it opens.

185
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:04,759
Perhaps

186
00:12:05,559 --> 00:12:06,240
I should try.

187
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:19,919
They even moved it to a different spot?

188
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,320
Is this the place?

189
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:31,799
The Immortal Gate rises,

190
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:33,399
the Celestial Realm returns.

191
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,279
All may tread the immortal path,

192
00:12:36,799 --> 00:12:38,799
all may receive blessings.

193
00:12:39,399 --> 00:12:40,639
According to ancestral records,

194
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,159
all eight Immortal Gates

195
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:44,879
should have risen by now.

196
00:12:45,679 --> 00:12:47,519
What on earth has gone wrong?

197
00:12:53,039 --> 00:12:55,240
When will our Shanhai City's Gate

198
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:59,240
finally appear?

199
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,559
It's risen into the sky.

200
00:13:20,279 --> 00:13:22,039
So the ancestral records were true.

201
00:13:22,639 --> 00:13:23,360
Go get them.

202
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,480
Tell them we're having a meeting.

203
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,799
Okay, I'll go get them.

204
00:13:31,399 --> 00:13:32,759
I knew it.

205
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,720
Just as I predicted.

206
00:13:35,279 --> 00:13:37,720
The gate in Shanhai City was delayed

207
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,360
because it's that important.

208
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:43,080
I don't know why they're in such a rush.

209
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,679
What's happening in the sky,

210
00:13:48,559 --> 00:13:49,480
you've all seen it, right?

211
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,360
The Celestial Realm hovers above.

212
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:53,440
If we find those with immortal affinity,

213
00:13:53,519 --> 00:13:55,159
we can bridge heaven and earth,

214
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,799
and summon the immortals directly.

215
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,480
What we can do

216
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:01,600
is let those without affinity ascend.

217
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,600
But to summon immortals,

218
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,679
we need a huge amount of money.

219
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,639
So, next,

220
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,440
we can first summon one immortal,

221
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,879
then recruit more members

222
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:14,799
to join our ranks,

223
00:14:14,799 --> 00:14:15,840
and keep expanding.

224
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:18,120
I've already chosen the person.

225
00:14:18,639 --> 00:14:19,600
His immortal affinity

226
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:22,039
is enough for our first sacrifice.

227
00:14:22,799 --> 00:14:23,840
After tonight,

228
00:14:24,279 --> 00:14:25,360
our Shanhai City

229
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:28,039
is bound to become a thorn in the side

230
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:31,039
of the eight main and minor cities.

231
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,559
From this moment on,

232
00:14:33,919 --> 00:14:37,159
our legend will spread across the world.

233
00:14:38,519 --> 00:14:40,000
We are the Immortal Envoys.

234
00:14:41,399 --> 00:14:42,679
But none of that matters anymore.

235
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,440
With the Main Gate,

236
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:47,799
we will enjoy supreme glory.

237
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,080
Sealed away for a thousand years,

238
00:14:57,559 --> 00:15:01,000
I can finally return to the mortal world.

239
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,240
Once all gates open,

240
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,840
my body will be restored.

241
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:09,279
I'll kill this bastard the moment I can.

242
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:10,440
That's right.

243
00:15:10,759 --> 00:15:12,679
How dare he threaten us.

244
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,039
So this is

245
00:15:14,799 --> 00:15:16,120
where you've been hiding.

246
00:15:18,159 --> 00:15:19,679
All beings shall forget.

247
00:15:20,559 --> 00:15:22,080
Only immortals remain in control.

248
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,679
This suffocating place,

249
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,759
I refuse to stay here a moment longer.

250
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:32,720
Goodbye.

251
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:34,559
What is he doing?

252
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:35,879
Get back here, now!

253
00:15:35,879 --> 00:15:36,759
What are you doing?

254
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:38,879
Fool!

255
00:15:41,039 --> 00:15:42,279
Get back here!

256
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:43,720
Come back!

257
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,039
Come back!

258
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,039
Is this

259
00:15:56,559 --> 00:16:00,000
a special effect of the Main Gate?

260
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,080
No.

261
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,519
Something must have gone wrong.

262
00:16:07,399 --> 00:16:09,320
Go check right away

263
00:16:09,399 --> 00:16:10,639
the location where the Main Gate appeared,

264
00:16:10,639 --> 00:16:12,960
and see if there's anyone unusual nearby.

265
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:13,960
Understood?

266
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,799
Get moving!

267
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:24,240
Shanhai City

268
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:27,559
is about to go on high alert.

269
00:16:37,559 --> 00:16:38,360
I told you,

270
00:16:39,679 --> 00:16:40,639
if I can open the gate,

271
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,039
I can close it too.

272
00:16:43,559 --> 00:16:44,559
I wasn't lying, was I?
